data.title: 准备以至少20秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The most impressive place I have visited is Shanghai Disneyland. I went here two years ago and felt the joy of childhood. The game items can make me feel a kind of relaxation and pleasure. Before I went here, I had been living in a fast-paced work and life. This makes me feel stressed and anxious. However, the experience of going to Disney made me feel relaxed physically and psychologically. The fireworks which showed at night brought me a kind of satisfaction, so this entertainment project made me have good memories. This is a unique place that I have ever visited and enjoyed.
data.referenceText: Describe a unique place that you have visited and enjoyed. What made this place notable?
data.referenceTranslate: 描述一个你去过并喜欢的独特的地方，是什么让这个地方引人注目。
